gobblin.example.wikipedia

Class WikipediaExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.example.wikipedia.WikipediaExtractor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Extractor<String,com.google.gson.JsonElement>, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class WikipediaExtractor
extends Object
implements Extractor<String,com.google.gson.JsonElement>
    An implementation of Extractor for the Wikipedia example.

    This extractor uses the MediaWiki web API to retrieve a certain number of latest revisions for each specified title from Wikipedia. Each revision is returned as a JSON document.
